  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GWFP Nitron 2019</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The facility is expected to continue having the following development impacts: (i) development of the agriculture sector in Latin America and Africa by increasing reliable fertilizer supply to farmers; (ii) improvement of crop yields in emerging markets; strengthening of financial integration of the fertilizer value chain in the markets where Nitron operates.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The proposed investment consists of an unfunded participation of USD 50 million by IFC in a trade finance facility (the Facility) in favor of Nitron Group Corporation (Nitron). The purpose of the facility is to finance the purchase, storage and transportation of fertilizers by Nitron for further sales to Latin America and Africa.</narrative>
  </description>
